  <steps>
    <step num="0">Preheat oven to 350˚F (180˚C). </step>
    <step num="1">In bowl, add the almonds, salt, cayenne, honey, and olive oil, and stir to combine. </step>
    <step num="2">Transfer to a parchment paper-lined baking sheet, and bake for 12 minutes, until the honey is caramelized and the almonds are aromatic. </step>
    <step num="3">Let cool. </step>
    <step num="4">Enjoy! </step>
  </steps>
